        </div>
Spinato's Pizzeria has been in business for over 40 years and offers a family oriented dining atmosphere. If you're looking to work for a company that values its employees as our most important assets, apply at Spinato's today! We offer a flexible, stable, fun, and family environment with opportunities for growth. <br>
<br>
Spinato's currently has part-time and full-time positions open for both the Front of House and Heart (Back) of the House at many of our locations.  <br>
<br>
Don't want to work nights or weekends?  Check out our opportunities for our Fine Foods Division.  We are looking for Pizza Line Production Family Members!  If you have more flexibility-check out our promotional specialist positions we have available with Fine Foods as well!<br>
<br>
Is Pastry your passion?  Check out our job opportunities with our Andiamo Market, located at our Central Phoenix Location!<br>
<br>
To see what positions each of our 5 locations and Fine Foods Division have available, visit our recruiting site via our company webpage at <a href="http://spinatospizzeria.com/join-the-family/" rel="nofollow">http://spinatospizzeria.com/join-the-family/</a> (located at bottom of web page) <br>
<br>
We are flexible and can work around school schedules and other obligations. Work environment is casual. <br>
<br>
Spinato's Employment Benefits:<br>
<br>
Closed all major holidays<br>
Work in a casual and friendly work environment<br>
Spinato's offers a free family-style meals for employees on every shift, and 25% discount on all meals for their immediate family!<br>
<br>
Spinato's Pizzeria uses e-verify<br>
<br>
Spinato's Pizzeria is an Equal Opportunity Employer.<br>
    </section>

